safetyTips: Contact-free delivery, leaving shopping at the door, knocking on the door then moving to a safe distance, to wait for the customer to open the door and pick up shopping.
name: Healthmatters Healthstore
description: We sell natural and herbal remedies, food supplements, probiotics, skincare, bath salts, and household products. We offer organic grains, seeds, nuts, dried fruits, plant-based milk, and wheat-free bread. Our aromatherapy range includes essential oils, candles, reed diffusers, and incense sticks. We have organic nut butter, low-GI fruit spreads, cider vinegar, cranberry, blueberry and apple juice. Our refill station includes shampoo, conditioner, body wash, washing-up liquid, detergent, fabric conditioner, toilet cleaner, and multipurpose cleaner. And we offer a wide choice of herbal teas including Pukka, Clipper, Yogi, Dragonfly, Tea Pigs and Celestial Teas.
